Media.


Features:

- fetch new releases (scene releases, tv schedule, music reviews)
- grab new media matching the filters (rating, genre, date, etc)
- grab similar media (directors movies, similar bands albums)
- grab movies and tv shows subtitles
- unpack and sort new media into the media type based directories
- fetch media metadata (director, release date, etc)
- fetch media trailers and audio tracks
- sync media to devices (laptop, phone)


Start the daemon and webui:
./media/run.py
